title: 660: CRYPTO ANALYST UNVEILS MASSIVE YEAR-END TARGETS FOR BITCOIN AND ETHEREUM!!!!!
description:
A popular crypto analyst says Bitcoin and Ethereum can pull off massive rallies before the end of 2021 as traders underestimate the second leg of the bull market.

Justin Bennett tells his 61,600 Twitter followers that he expects Bitcoin to launch a staggering rally, well above the six-figure level, should the leading cryptocurrency shatter its current ATH of $65,000.
